reviewText: Aside from Transformers I am an El Mongo fan of Ed Edd n Eddy. I just love this show. All the characters always make me laugh. I wish Cartoon Network would have a contest where you could be on the show (or at least being animated into a character). All my friends and I love this show and we can't get enough of em. I hope that they return for a sixth season. I also hope they make one as a refrence to Indiana Jones (like Indiana Ed or Ediana Jones etc). There is an Movie coming out where they try to find Eddy's older brother (who  is the only unseen character aside from the adults hands). So I GOT to get these die hard funny movies. ED EDD N EDDY BOOO YEAHHHHH!!!

Title: Ed Edd & Eddy - The Complete Seasons 1&2

reviewText: I bought mine new. They came with a listing of shows for each season. Highlights of the series are any episodes which feature the Kanker Sisters, especially "Avast Ye Eds" and "Honor Thy Ed".Special features on disc 1 - How to Make an Ed, Edd n Eddy Cartoon; Interview with the Creator; How to Draw Eddy; Cartoon Network Promos "28 Days Later" and "Crybaby", featuring Jimmy. All the features on disc 1 are fun.Special features on disc 2 - "Behind the Eds" with the show's creator; How to draw Ed; Music video: "I'm Not Coming In Today"; Cartoon Network Promos "Ed's Origami" and "The Good the Bad and the Ugly". These are fun, also.The features are a nice addition. They are fun. The show's creator, Danny Antonucci, is a blast.
